00:17.936 --> 00:19.028
[Grunts]

00:31.816 --> 00:33.306
[Gasping]

00:33.385 --> 00:35.319
[Panting]

00:35.387 --> 00:37.548
Can you hear me?

00:39.958 --> 00:41.949
- What happened?
- You nearly died.

00:42.027 --> 00:43.927
Your brain was almost out of oxygen.

00:43.995 --> 00:46.429
You'll be seeing black spots
for the next few days.

00:46.498 --> 00:49.058
The rest of your senses
will recover naturally.

00:49.134 --> 00:51.261
[Coughs]
Did it work?

00:51.336 --> 00:53.099
Did they come?

00:54.839 --> 00:56.739
No, Mr. Walker.

01:04.182 --> 01:06.946
There was no visitation.

01:16.828 --> 01:18.853
<i>I waited as long as I could...</i>

01:18.930 --> 01:21.296
but finally, I had to revive you.

01:27.839 --> 01:30.808
They seem to have repaired
the damage done by the bullet.

01:30.875 --> 01:32.604
[Dry Laugh]

01:33.945 --> 01:35.606
How did you get in here?

01:35.680 --> 01:38.615
I go where Grace goes.
I've been charged to protect her.

01:39.984 --> 01:41.952
Have you?

01:42.020 --> 01:44.011
You can't even protect yourself.

01:44.089 --> 01:46.455
They may have given you speech, Pepper.

01:46.524 --> 01:48.219
Even a parrot can be taught to mimic.

01:48.293 --> 01:50.784
But did they give you
the capacity to think?

01:50.862 --> 01:52.659
I sincerely doubt it.

01:54.532 --> 01:57.365
Tell me, Polly...
What did they put inside her?

01:57.435 --> 01:59.494
I won't tell you anything.

01:59.571 --> 02:01.539
If you're not going to tell me...

02:01.606 --> 02:04.666
then I'll just have to find out
for myself, won't I?

02:04.742 --> 02:07.302
X-rays will harm
the life growing inside of her.

02:07.378 --> 02:10.745
- That's a chance I'm willing to take.
- Stupid man.

02:10.815 --> 02:14.012
You think they'd allow you to continue
your barbaric practice?

02:14.085 --> 02:15.643
She's protected.

02:15.720 --> 02:19.019
Your X-rays won't penetrate her body.
You'll see nothing.

02:19.090 --> 02:20.648
Oh, but they've been watching you.

02:20.725 --> 02:24.161
You think you're like them,
with your clumsy experiments.

02:24.229 --> 02:26.493
But they laugh at you, Dr. Arden.

02:26.564 --> 02:28.259
They make jokes.

02:29.334 --> 02:30.323
Here's a good one.

02:30.401 --> 02:31.732
Knock, knock. Who's there?

02:31.803 --> 02:33.202
Arden. Arden who?

02:33.271 --> 02:36.502
Arden you the quack
who'd make a better duck? [Laughs]

02:36.574 --> 02:38.064
Huh.

02:38.143 --> 02:40.236
Well, if taking X-rays won't work...

02:40.311 --> 02:42.677
perhaps more invasive observation will.

02:42.747 --> 02:46.513
I think her condition calls
for an emergency C-section, don't you?

02:46.584 --> 02:48.074
You can't do that.

02:50.155 --> 02:51.554
Watch me.

02:52.657 --> 02:53.783
[Scalpel Clatters]

02:55.326 --> 02:57.794
Dr. Arden, you still see me
as microcephalic.

02:57.862 --> 02:59.420
No one takes a pinhead seriously.

02:59.497 --> 03:02.830
When my sister's husband drowned her baby
and sliced his ears off...

03:02.901 --> 03:04.391
he told everyone I did it.

03:04.469 --> 03:07.461
They tied me up and paraded me
in front of the judge.

03:07.539 --> 03:12.272
He took one look at the shape of my head,
and I was locked up for good.

03:12.343 --> 03:15.039
That's how it works with us freaks.
We get blamed for everything.

03:15.113 --> 03:17.411
But if something happens
to Grace in here...

03:17.482 --> 03:19.643
and she's harmed in <i>any</i> way...

03:19.717 --> 03:21.708
there won't be anyone else to blame.

03:21.786 --> 03:23.276
They'll take you...

03:23.354 --> 03:26.619
open up your head
and stir your brain with a fork.

03:27.692 --> 03:29.319
Then, when you return...

03:29.394 --> 03:32.124
you'll experience firsthand
how people treat us freaks.

03:32.197 --> 03:34.290
I'll take care of Grace.

03:35.700 --> 03:37.429
Why don't you go to your whore nun...

03:37.502 --> 03:39.834
have her soothe your deflated ego?

03:39.904 --> 03:42.065
[Gasping]

03:53.251 --> 03:55.515
<i>[Thunderclap]</i>

04:49.507 --> 04:54.001
I'm haunted by the idea
that Lee Emerson is still at large.

04:54.078 --> 04:55.568
Believe me, Monsignor...

04:55.647 --> 04:58.411
finding Lee Emerson is a top priority.

04:58.483 --> 05:00.883
They're searching for him
in five different states.

05:00.952 --> 05:02.385
It's a huge manhunt.

05:02.453 --> 05:06.048
I'm filled with remorse
at my blindness about him.

05:06.124 --> 05:08.149
You are not to blame.

05:21.673 --> 05:23.368
I'll be sleeping right there...

05:23.441 --> 05:25.432
if you need something during the night.

05:27.278 --> 05:29.246
<i>[Monsignor Howard]
Have you come for me?</i>

05:34.619 --> 05:36.450
Why are you here?

05:36.521 --> 05:39.046
You have more work to do.

05:39.123 --> 05:42.183
The devil lives at Briarcliff
in your favorite young nun.

05:42.260 --> 05:44.228
You must cast her out.

05:46.931 --> 05:48.762
<i>[Monsignor Howard]
I'm too weak.</i>

05:49.967 --> 05:53.596
- God will help you.
- She'll know.

05:53.671 --> 05:56.936
Guard your thoughts. Use your rosary.

05:58.109 --> 05:59.940
<i>Each bead is his name.</i>

06:03.181 --> 06:05.547
This is your moment, Timothy.

06:06.584 --> 06:09.052
Thank you for everything, Sister.

06:10.488 --> 06:12.285
I'll be back later.

06:12.357 --> 06:15.326
I have to oversee a delivery.

06:15.393 --> 06:17.623
Exciting new things
are happening around here.

06:21.132 --> 06:23.225
[No Audible Dialogue]

06:24.535 --> 06:26.059
[Door Shuts]

06:26.137 --> 06:28.298
[Chattering]

06:30.174 --> 06:32.506
She's doing this to taunt me.

06:34.812 --> 06:37.610
[Whistle Blowing]

06:37.682 --> 06:40.480
People! I have an announcement to make.

06:40.551 --> 06:43.543
As most of you know, recently
our beloved recording of "Dominique"...

06:43.621 --> 06:46.317
was smashed to pieces by someone...

06:46.391 --> 06:48.086
who shall remain nameless.

06:48.159 --> 06:52.789
In fact, I'll just call her
patient number G2573.

06:52.864 --> 06:54.764
But rather than allow...

06:54.832 --> 06:57.096
one bitter woman's
actions ruin things for everyone...

06:57.168 --> 07:00.001
I've decided to take this opportunity...

07:00.071 --> 07:03.336
to bring Briarcliff into the 20th century.

07:03.408 --> 07:05.968
I dug into our rainy-day fund...

07:06.043 --> 07:10.207
and bought this beautiful used jukebox.

07:10.281 --> 07:13.808
I'm sure there's something in there
that can appeal to everyone's taste.

07:13.885 --> 07:16.376
Camels? A pack of Camels?

07:16.454 --> 07:20.447
No, Gerard. It's not a cigarette machine.

07:20.525 --> 07:23.289
It's a great big music box!

07:23.361 --> 07:26.524
And for our maiden number,
I would like to dedicate this one...

07:26.597 --> 07:30.829
to our newest resident,
patient number G2573...

07:30.902 --> 07:34.895
Miss Judy Martin.

07:34.972 --> 07:38.567
- <i>[Chorus] # Ooh, spell #</i>
- Enjoy.

07:38.643 --> 07:42.135
That's your name? Judy Martin?

07:42.213 --> 07:45.671
Not anymore.
We're all just numbers here.

07:45.750 --> 07:47.741
<i>[Man]
# I put a spell on you #</i>

07:47.819 --> 07:49.912
<i>[Chorus]
# Ooh, spell #</i>

07:51.222 --> 07:53.986
<i># Ooh, spell #</i>

07:55.059 --> 07:57.721
<i># 'Cause you're mine #</i>

07:57.795 --> 08:00.059
<i># Ooh, spell #</i>

08:01.599 --> 08:04.033
<i># Ooh, spell #</i>

08:04.101 --> 08:06.092
Come on.

08:06.170 --> 08:08.400
<i># Stop the things you do #</i>

08:08.473 --> 08:11.533
[Whispering]
We have to talk.

08:13.511 --> 08:16.344
- Something's happened.
- Thredson's loose.

08:16.414 --> 08:17.779
How do you know that?

08:17.849 --> 08:19.612
<i># Watch out #</i>

08:19.684 --> 08:22.949
<i># I ain't lyin'#</i>

08:25.890 --> 08:27.858
<i>##[Singer Screams]</i>

08:27.925 --> 08:31.361
- How'd he get out?
- <i>[Singer] Whool Whoo.</i>

08:31.429 --> 08:32.919
Son of a bitch.

08:32.996 --> 08:35.124
<i>##[Continues, Faint]</i>

08:38.135 --> 08:40.763
Well, well, well, well, well.

08:42.539 --> 08:44.474
Isn't this pleasant,
the three of us sitting around...

08:44.542 --> 08:46.373
like civilized people?

08:49.614 --> 08:52.310
That's a wise move.
I was about to bash your face in.

08:52.383 --> 08:54.010
Hmm.

08:54.085 --> 08:55.746
I know you were.

08:55.820 --> 08:57.879
I admire your pluck.

08:57.955 --> 09:00.253
It's a quality
I hope you'll pass on to our child.

09:01.392 --> 09:02.984
Oh, she didn't tell you either?

09:03.060 --> 09:05.494
Her attempts to self-abort
proved fruitless.

09:05.563 --> 09:09.260
Our baby's strong, Lana. A survivor.

09:09.333 --> 09:11.824
And he's the only thing
that's keeping you alive right now.

09:11.903 --> 09:14.235
As long as he's growing
inside of your womb, you're safe.

09:14.305 --> 09:16.899
Then what happens? You murder me?

09:16.974 --> 09:19.169
Oh, no. I'll have to keep you around...

09:19.243 --> 09:21.108
to breast-feed that baby
for at least the first year.

09:21.178 --> 09:22.668
The health benefits are myriad.

09:22.747 --> 09:25.113
You are one sick twist.

09:26.584 --> 09:30.111
And you're a wanted man.
I wonder if they're offering a reward.

09:30.187 --> 09:31.677
Find out. Turn me in.

09:31.756 --> 09:33.621
Hmm.
You'd like that, wouldn't you?

09:33.691 --> 09:35.158
Go to the police...

09:35.226 --> 09:37.592
and your illegally obtained,
taped confession goes with you.

09:38.763 --> 09:42.164
We can discuss that
and other issues tomorrow...

09:42.233 --> 09:43.700
when we resume your treatment.

09:44.969 --> 09:47.733
That's right.
Sister Mary Eunice has offered me...

09:47.805 --> 09:50.035
a full-time position here at Briarcliff.

09:50.107 --> 09:52.632
She's a remarkably forward-thinking
administrator for a nun...

09:52.710 --> 09:56.669
and surprisingly adept
at untying slipknots.

09:56.747 --> 09:58.442
<i>#... Spell on you #</i>

10:00.618 --> 10:03.212
- <i>[Chorus] # Spell ##</i>
- <i>##[Singer Screams]</i>

10:03.354 --> 10:04.719
[Patient Screams]

10:04.789 --> 10:07.314
- [Banging]
- [Carl] Everybody up and out now!

10:07.391 --> 10:09.222
- [Door Opens]
- [Patients Chattering]

10:09.293 --> 10:11.124
Move. Move. Let's go. Get up.

10:11.195 --> 10:12.958
- [Woman Shrieks]
- Step out.

10:13.030 --> 10:15.328
- [Man] You heard him.
- [Carl] Open those doors.

10:17.201 --> 10:18.691
Get out here.

10:20.638 --> 10:21.832
[Cackling]

10:21.906 --> 10:23.396
Open your door.

10:25.376 --> 10:27.071
Christine.

10:30.448 --> 10:31.915
Room search, ladies.

10:33.417 --> 10:35.977
We find it keeps our charges honest.

10:36.053 --> 10:37.543
You mocking me?

10:37.622 --> 10:40.090
I don't have time to mock you, Judy.
I have work to do.

10:40.157 --> 10:42.853
A lot of work,
given your epic failure here.

10:42.927 --> 10:45.327
You gave him a job? Are you insane?

10:45.396 --> 10:47.830
- Guards!
- Whoa, whoa.

10:47.898 --> 10:50.992
Dr. Thredson is on the cutting edge
of psychiatric medicine.

10:51.068 --> 10:52.558
We need a guy like him around here...

10:52.637 --> 10:54.264
to whip this place into shape.

10:54.338 --> 10:56.602
Yeah, well, he's here for me,
and you know it.

10:56.674 --> 11:00.041
And when he murders me...
which he will... you will be responsible.

11:00.111 --> 11:03.569
Oh. Quite the contrary, Miss Winters.

11:03.648 --> 11:07.379
Dr. Thredson is concerned for you...
and for your unborn child.

11:08.419 --> 11:10.410
- Take her to hydrotherapy.
- No.

11:10.488 --> 11:12.854
Strip her down
and boil her for 20 minutes.

11:12.923 --> 11:14.584
No!

11:16.761 --> 11:19.093
Anyone else have a bone to pick with me?

11:19.163 --> 11:21.131
I do.

11:21.198 --> 11:23.894
[Chuckles]
I bet you do, Judy.

11:24.935 --> 11:26.425
Let's have a look in your room.

11:26.504 --> 11:28.768
Fine. There's nothing in there.

11:33.477 --> 11:35.741
Judy, Judy, Judy.

11:35.813 --> 11:37.405
[Giggling]

11:37.481 --> 11:39.608
Did you steal this from the kitchen?

11:39.684 --> 11:42.278
I bet you got the idea from Shelley.

11:42.353 --> 11:44.583
[Dry Chuckle]
Very funny.

11:45.656 --> 11:47.920
Do you think about the monsignor?

11:47.992 --> 11:49.755
[Whispering]
Vile thing.

11:50.628 --> 11:52.721
This is awkward for me...

11:52.797 --> 11:55.425
given our prior relationship...

11:55.499 --> 11:58.798
but I can't have you
diddling yourself all night long.

11:58.869 --> 12:00.427
So punish me.

12:05.476 --> 12:08.343
[Grunting]
No, goddamn you. Let me go!

12:08.412 --> 12:09.970
This is sadism!

12:10.047 --> 12:13.278
Quite the contrary. You've exhibited
clear-cut signs of manic depression...

12:13.350 --> 12:15.477
for which electroshock therapy...

12:15.553 --> 12:16.986
- is the prescribed treatment.
- No!

12:17.054 --> 12:20.512
Just look at Miss Winters.
It completely cured her gynephilia.

12:20.591 --> 12:22.024
[Sister Jude]
Sister.

12:22.093 --> 12:24.960
Sister, I know somewhere in there
you can hear me.

12:25.029 --> 12:27.327
This is wrong. It's wrong. It's wrong.

12:27.398 --> 12:29.992
You know it's wrong!

12:30.067 --> 12:31.694
[Groaning]

12:31.769 --> 12:34.203
- [Gags]
- Oh, Jude.

12:34.271 --> 12:36.466
We're gonna burn those
bad memories right out of you.

12:36.540 --> 12:39.338
That runaway groom,
those drunken blackouts...

12:39.410 --> 12:42.004
all of it gone in a wisp of smoke.

12:43.247 --> 12:45.374
[Arden]
She's right, you know.

12:45.449 --> 12:49.146
Most patients experience
a sense of euphoria after the treatment.

12:49.220 --> 12:52.656
- May I, Doctor?
- Yes, you may. No higher than 50%.

12:54.024 --> 12:55.685
[Electrical Humming]

12:55.760 --> 12:57.455
- [Moaning, Gasping]
- She's one tough cookie.

12:58.395 --> 13:00.124
She may need a little extra.

13:00.197 --> 13:02.563
- [Gasping]
- [Humming Intensifies]

13:02.633 --> 13:04.123
On.

13:05.736 --> 13:08.796
- [Electricity Crackling]
- [Muffled Screaming]

13:27.291 --> 13:28.781
Oh.

13:29.994 --> 13:31.985
Oh, it's healing quite well.

13:32.897 --> 13:35.024
Too well if you ask me.

13:36.033 --> 13:37.694
What could you mean by that?

13:37.768 --> 13:42.296
After showing such kindness
to a guttersnipe like Lee Emerson...

13:42.373 --> 13:44.204
you deserve to be canonized.

13:44.275 --> 13:47.369
These marks befit a future saint like you.

13:47.444 --> 13:50.038
I command you, unclean spirit
now attacking this servant of God...

13:50.114 --> 13:53.550
to obey me to the letter...
I, who am a minister of God...

13:53.617 --> 13:57.246
Yeah, good one, Father.
You want to hear mine?

13:57.321 --> 14:00.882
There was a priest, the dirty beast,
whose name was Alexander.

14:00.958 --> 14:02.755
His mighty dick was inches thick.

14:02.827 --> 14:05.227
He called it Salamander.

14:05.296 --> 14:07.764
In Jesus' name I command...

14:11.168 --> 14:12.965
Is yours inches thick...

14:14.772 --> 14:16.262
Father?

14:16.340 --> 14:17.864
[Ragged Breathing]

14:17.942 --> 14:19.569
Stop it, please.

14:19.643 --> 14:21.736
Mmm.

14:21.812 --> 14:23.370
Your body disagrees with you.

14:23.447 --> 14:24.607
I...

14:26.283 --> 14:28.410
- I took a vow.
- Mmm.

14:28.485 --> 14:30.715
You don't say that with much conviction.

14:30.788 --> 14:32.813
Please. Don't do this to me.

14:34.091 --> 14:35.956
The Church means...

14:36.961 --> 14:38.929
everything to me.

14:38.996 --> 14:41.487
It's okay. We're like Adam and Eve...

14:41.565 --> 14:43.624
two innocent children...

14:43.701 --> 14:46.499
discovering each other's bodies
for the first time.

14:50.708 --> 14:54.610
- This is your first time, isn't it?
- Yes.

14:54.678 --> 14:57.408
I gave my body...

14:57.481 --> 14:59.312
to... Christ!

14:59.383 --> 15:01.078
What has he given to you?

15:02.319 --> 15:04.844
Oh, come on, Father.

15:04.922 --> 15:07.482
Don't you want to feel what it's like...

15:08.759 --> 15:11.922
at least once... before you die?

15:11.996 --> 15:14.624
[Groans]

15:14.698 --> 15:17.667
[Gasps]
Does it feel like a warm...

15:17.735 --> 15:19.965
wet... hug?

15:20.537 --> 15:22.095
God, no.

15:22.172 --> 15:25.972
You have to stop.

15:26.043 --> 15:28.136
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

15:28.946 --> 15:31.141
No!
[Groans]

15:31.215 --> 15:34.446
No, no.
No, don't do it. Don't do it yet.

15:35.519 --> 15:37.350
[Yells]

15:39.623 --> 15:43.616
<i>##[Rock Intro]</i>

15:43.694 --> 15:46.389
<i>##[Chorus Vocalizing]</i>

15:49.967 --> 15:52.128
