15:56.373 --> 15:57.897
<i>##[Man Singing, Faint]</i>

15:57.975 --> 15:59.465
[Whispering]
Holy shit.

15:59.543 --> 16:02.011
[Chattering Voices Echoing]

16:02.079 --> 16:04.343
[Laughter Echoing]

16:08.886 --> 16:11.377
Looks like they turned
the juice up extra high.

16:14.825 --> 16:16.725
Why doesn't it make me feel any better?

16:22.633 --> 16:25.295
<i># Yeah, way deep in love #</i>

